<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> pukaḻ [mātu puṇara <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yamātu] virumpa <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> Avanimuḻutuṭai
<lb n="2" break="no"/><unclear>yā</unclear>ḷoṭum viṟṟiruntaruḷiya kovirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ke<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>ripa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi>rāta cakkaravattikaḷ <gap reason="lost" quantity="13" unit="character"/> yāṇṭu pat <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> perum puliyūr tiruvāykkula muṭaiyāṉum cempiya
<lb n="3" break="no"/><unclear>nmā</unclear>tevi Aḻakiyama <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> nampiyum ceṇpakanārāyaṇa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> viranārāyaṇa caruppeti maṅkalattu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ṇakarc caruppetimaṅkalattu <gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/> nampiyum Ippaṇṭāravāriyam Āritan kuru <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> palaṉ Ārāvamutum Āritan ti
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ruvāykkulamu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Āritan kecuvan <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> tiru veṅkaṭamum pāratāyan <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> num pā<supplied reason="omitted">ra</supplied>tāyan Ārāvamutu cirā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> kkaṇakkup peru<unclear>mpu</unclear>ṟakkaṭal ko <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> vāmanaṉāna pe <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>piriya <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> varaṅka<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>va <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> piriyanum <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> Āḻvānukku munpu Amutu paṭikku <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kal veṭṭuppaṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> pu naṭa viṭṭa tirukka<note n="50-1">The rest is lost.</note>
</p>

<p>By the side of this is the begining of another inscription commencing:</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> pūmātu viḷaṅka <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ya <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>nampi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> yār cilaiyan kuntavai <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>cāmuṇṭan kovarttana maṇavā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

